    <header class="aboutusheader">
        <div class="aboutusheader__content">
            <h1 class="heading--h2 color--white">We are on a mission to make sure no person ever goes to an interview
                unprepared.</h1>
            <p class="base--20 color--white">A Job Aspirant on average goes through 4 interviews, waits for 6 months
                until he lands a job, and goes through this process 5-6 times in their lifetime. The biggest reason for
                this is the lack of preparation and access to feedback.</p>
        </div>
    </header>
    <section class="section ourstory--section">
        <div class="wrapper">
            <div class="ourstorygrid">
                <div class="ourstorygrid__info">
                    <h2 class="ourstorygrid__info--h2 heading--h2">Our Story</h2>
                    <p class="ourstorygrid__info--p base--18">InterviewBuddy was conceived in 2017 when we found from
                        our own personal experience that even smart people get stumped at interviews. We realized that
                        anyone can become awesome at interviewing with practice and taking practice mock interviews.
                        These skills can be honed by getting mentored by experts and 94.83% of our users found positive
                        results after taking practice mock interviews. </p>
                    <p class="ourstorygrid__info--p base--18">We're based out of a small quaint coastal town
                        Visakhapatnam in the southern part of India. We feel a sense of pride knowing that we were able
                        to touch the lives of our users staying on the other side of the planet, studying in Ivy-league
                        universities like Stanford, Harvard and Georgia-Tech.</p>
                    <p class="ourstorygrid__info--p base--18">Enabled by an entirely seamless online experience, we
                        created\attracted a strong global community of experts hand-holding students and professionals
                        on their career paths. Not to boast, but we take immense pride in our 1500+ strong community of
                        global experts, clocking 1500000+ hours of online practice interviews on our platform and
                        helping 40000+ students and professionals get placed in 500+ global companies, organizations and
                        startups.</p>
                    <!-- <p class="ourstorygrid__info--p base--18">Our mock interviews are conducted by handpicked industry
                        experts with an average experience of 9+ years in the interviewing game. So youâ€™re sure to
                        improve your chances of getting hired!</p> -->
                </div>
                <div class="ourstorygrid__graphic"><img class="ourstorygrid__graphic--img"
                        src="assets/images/ac7dd03413ded3e488fb.png" alt="ourstory"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
